of arrangements of approaching pseudo-lines (while there are only $2^{\Theta(n
\log n)}$ isomorphism classes of line arrangements). 2. It can be decided in
polynomial time whether an allowable sequence is realizable by an arrangement
of approaching pseudo-lines.
