one-dimensional linear advection-diffusion-reaction equation in a layered
medium. Our solution approach involves introducing unknown functions
representing the diffusive flux at the interfaces between adjacent layers,
allowing the multilayer problem to be solved separately on each layer in the
Laplace domain before being numerically inverted back to the time domain. The
